  "detailed_description": "<i>New kind of adventure</i> is a 3D adventure game with RPG elements. <br>Mary hides in a wardrobe after her parents had a fight. She falls asleep. When Mary awakes, she discovers that she is in a beautiful, magical world with giant strawberries and magical druids!<br>With her new friend Aquarius, Mary must find a way back to the real world!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use Mary's new found powers and Aquarius' magical abilities to solve puzzles and complete quests.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect Artefacts to unlock new magical powers and abilities.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A huge vibrant world, with colourful wildlife and environments.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gather items and resources to trade with Druids.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Original folk jam soundtrack. </li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>New kind of adventure</i> is a 3D adventure game with RPG elements. <br>Mary hides in a wardrobe after her parents had a fight. She falls asleep. When Mary awakes, she discovers that she is in a beautiful, magical world with giant strawberries and magical druids!<br>With her new friend Aquarius, Mary must find a way back to the real world!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use Mary's new found powers and Aquarius' magical abilities to solve puzzles and complete quests.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect Artefacts to unlock new magical powers and abilities.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A huge vibrant world, with colourful wildlife and environments.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gather items and resources to trade with Druids.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Original folk jam soundtrack. </li></ul>",
